{"tid":2033350,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"#SOS4HK Campaign國際戰線！","createTime":"2020-05-24T15:06:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-24T15:13:31.000Z","uid":287572,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"9af26e3a7cee28fd23761fd18cbda41025ed9b95","tid":2033350,"uid":287572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T15:06:08.000Z","msg":"呢幾日Twitter都熱鬧左好多，我地要乘住個勢上，宣布啟動#SOS4HK campaign！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地既目標係要令香港再次上Twitter trending！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n記唔記得上年六月同929我地有超過50個城巿舉行反送中遊行，成功connect全世界手足？<br />\n<br />\n雖然依家受疫情影響，有好多海外手足唔可以搞遊行，但係我地要繼續用其他方式集氣，全力打國際戰線！！！<br />\n<br />\n上一次既#eye4hk campaign我地成功connect左好多國家既人，甚至連以色列既人都有join我地既campaign！<br />\n<br />\n其實之前一班文宣手足巳經發起過相似活動，而日本京成電鐵都率先發起左網上支持香港既行動，我地要keep住個勢，展現我地比五毛更加強既網絡力量！！！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DnwhzNQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDnwhzNQ.jpg&h=2dcc3b46&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢個活動門檻好低，但又draw到外國人既attention, 令到外國人又一個被動淨係睇新聞既角色，轉化成為我地既一份子！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n#SOS4HK參與方法<br />\n用手掩住口鼻，自拍一張！<br />\n<br />\n呢個手勢明確反映係國安法下，香港人會面對既白色恐怖，同時希望令更多外國人知道呢件事既迫切性！！！<br />\n<br />\n我地要post 上Twitter, Reddit, Facebook 同 Instagram, 再tag兩個frd，如此類推！！記住tag埋你d海外朋友！<br />\n<br />\n根據大家既反應同意見，我地會定一個日期同時間一齊轟炸social media！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nTags:<br />\n#SOS4HK<br />\n#SOSForHK<br />\n#NationalSecurityLaw<br />\n#FreeHongKong<br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命<br />\n香港獨立，唯一出路"},{"pid":"de50d05dc4696c4d32d3237ddda5821aaaa9e3b2","tid":2033350,"uid":287572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T15:13:31.000Z","msg":"pishhhhh <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}